	directAnswerHtml={`<strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">If you're single, the Father's Heart Bible™ is for you.</strong> You may carry more than people see — the quiet ache for a partner, the loneliness on a long evening, the pressure from family or church, the fatigue of one more dating app, the wondering whether God forgot you. The <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Father's Heart Bible™</a> is a fresh English translation you can read and <em>listen to</em> free on your phone — and it reveals God as a <em>Father</em> from beginning to end. Whether you searched "Bible verses for singles," "verses for single women" or "single men," "contentment," "waiting on God," or "does God have a plan for me" — the answer starts in one place: you are not incomplete and you are not behind. You are His beloved, fully loved and fully home in Him, right now — not someday when life finally looks different.`}
