	aFatherHeading={`A Father for singles`}
	aFatherBodyHtml={`<p>Here's what almost no one tells you in the middle of a single season: the answer to the ache isn't finally meeting someone, fixing your profile, or becoming the person you think a partner would want. The answer is a <strong style="color: var(--color-ink);">Father</strong> — a perfect, holy Father who already loves you, today, exactly as you are.</p><p>You were not made to wait for your worth. You were made to receive it. And the One who made you doesn't rank you by your relationship status, doesn't see you as half a person waiting to be completed, and doesn't love you any less because there's no ring on your hand. He calls you His beloved child — not the married you, not the someday you, but <em>you</em>, right now, in this exact season.</p><p>So before you are single, dating, divorced, or widowed — you are His. Your heavenly Father wants to be the steady presence in the quiet evenings, the One who fills the spaces you thought only a partner could fill, the voice that says: I see you, I'm with you, and you are fully home in Me.</p>`}
