		{ question: `What makes the Father's Heart Bible™ different for singles?`, answer: `It's the first English translation to reveal God as Father wherever Scripture reveals Him as Father — so instead of reading one more voice tying your worth to your relationship status, you meet the One who already calls you His beloved. For a single adult under pressure to be partnered, that reframes everything: you come to the Bible fully loved and fully home in Him, not as a person waiting to be completed.` },
